Ticket Description:
If this is a know Access Point and you wish to stop getting these alerts.
 * Consult with a senior tech!
 * Log into the UniFi Controller. 
 * Make sure you are using 'Legacy Mode'. 
 * Under 'Insight' on the left 
 * pick 'Neighboring Access Point' in the upper right hand drop down list
 * Look for a AP that has a red dot in the 'Rouge' Column 
 * On the far right of that row, when you hoover over it, the words 'Mark as known' will appear. Pick it. 
 * Archive all Rogue AP alerts under 'Alerts'

Notes: Maybe have all LTE events about Limits and Thresholds to be on 1 ticket
